@Node "Source" "Source"

Source
------

The Sources are included. You may use Parts of them in your own Projects,
but please mention me in your 'Credits' Section then.

If you have some Tips or Comments about the Code then please mail to @{" me " Link "Autor"}.

The Code was made with StormC V3.
To compile with StormC you have to install the stormamiga.lib-Packet (by Matthias
Henze, http://www.CyberdyneSystems.de/ ), or you must comment out the
Part '#ifdef __STORM__ ... #endif' in the Sources.

INLINE, REG and SAVEDS are defined in GUI.h and might have to be changed
depending on which compiler you use.

@EndNode

@Node "Bugs" "Known Bugs"

Known Bugs
----------

* If you open the MUI-Prefs with the Gadget in the Windowborder,
  the first two characters in the Popup where you can select Presets
  won't appear.
  This Problem comes and goes as it wants...

* The ImageButtons don't always have all the same size when the
  Textlengths are different.

* The Symbols in the Evaluation Column aren't Transparent.

* The Symbols in the Symbols Column don't line up if they don't have
  all the same size.

If you find furter Bugs or have Tips how to fix them,
please write to @{" me " Link "Autor"}.

